## Alias Syntax

What if you want to pull `user.name`, but the variable `name` is already taken in your app?

You can pull the exact key, but instantly alias (rename) it inside the Destructuring block using a colon `:`! 

```javascript
let user = { name: "Alice", age: 25 };

// We are pulling the 'name' key, but renaming it to 'firstName'
let { name: firstName, age } = user;

console.log(firstName); // Prints: Alice
```

This is a highly advanced trick used extensively in React!
